data.description: Welcome to this tranquil home nestled on a 1/3 acre lot in the heart of Suffolk! Don't miss out on this 5 bedroom/3 full bath 3000 sq. ft expansive home that offers both a spacious and open floor plan. The vaulted ceilings create a dramatic feel upon entry with an open loft above.This home offers 2 downstairs bedrooms, with full baths including an owner's en-suite with private bath, which includes a double vanity sink, separate tub and shower.
